  "content": "\n \n \n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.6em; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">最近行业里讨论一些新闻，挺热烈。很多揣测令人哭笑不得。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.6em; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">正好今天 The Information 发了一篇文章，我们转过来分享一下。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.6em; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">祝大家工作顺利。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.6em; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n   <span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.6em; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">本文来源 The Information，原文标题：OpenAI 与投资人关注华人创办的 AI Agent 公司（OpenAI, Investors Eye Agent Startups Led by Chinese Founders）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.6em; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">以下是翻译后的文章。</span></span></p><ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 1.5em; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n  </ul>\n  <hr style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 0.578px; border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); transform-origin: 0px 0px; transform: scale(1, 0.5); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 40px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.6em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">在 Manus 之后，华人创业者推出的 AI Agent 正引起硅谷的关注，甚至包括 OpenAI。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.6em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">Manus 是一款由华人创始人开发、能够使用浏览器的一款 agent 产品，在今年早些时候曾短暂爆红，并获得了 Benchmark 的资金支持。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.6em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">Genspark、Lovart、Flowith 和 Fellou，这些由华人创业者开发的 agent 产品，旨在实现将各类任务自动化，例如处理分析研究并将其结果转为 Excel 和 PPT，或是管理日程、预约和规划行程。Agent 背后的模型支持来自 Anthropic、OpenAI 及其他供应商的 AI 模型和工具。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.6em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">这其中，也有一些专注于需要艺术和设计专业知识的创意类产品。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.6em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">例如，处理设计相关任务的 Lovart 可以帮助咖啡馆老板构思品牌概念，以及店铺的标志、室内设计、周边商品包装和营销内容（如图片和视频）等。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.6em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">Lovart 创始人陈冕表示，「我们有机会运营一款全球性的产品。」他曾是字节跳动的高管，帮助这家公司的视频编辑应用 CapCut 成为全球爆款。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.6em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">陈冕称，Lovart 于今年五月发布的小范围测试版本，在五天内就吸引了超过 10 万名注册用户。Lovart 在加州的团队目前正准备在本月晚些时候发布 Lovart 正式版。据悉，公司计划与曾设计苹果公司第一款鼠标的美国设计公司 Ideo 在旧金山共同举办一场发布派对。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.6em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">由搜索巨头百度的前高管创立的公司 Genspark，在今年四月份发布了一款名为 Super Agent 的通用 AI agent，并在此后陆续更新，添加了许多新产品功能。例如，该 agent 能够通过分析原始数据、学术论文和网站，基于此制作 PPT，其中还可以嵌入从 YouTube 收集的相关视频。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.6em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">Genspark 还表示，它可以代表客户打电话预订餐厅或预约牙医的时间，甚至在一个案例中，可以帮助用户向其雇主提出辞职。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.6em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">据 Genspark 官方消息，在 Super Agent 发布后的 45 天内，其年度经常性收入（ARR）达到了 3600 万美元。Super Agent 服务的定价为每月 25 美元或每年 250 美元，这意味着它至少拥有 14.4 万名付费客户。据 Generative AI Database 的数据，这家成立两年的公司已经融资了 1.6 亿美元。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.6em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">上周，OpenAI 发表了一篇关于 Genspark 的博文，提到该公司使用了 OpenAI 的 GPT-4.1 和实时语音模型。 在此之前，Anthropic 也曾将 Genspark 作为典型案例在官网进行推介。</span></span></p>\n  <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.6em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/00819a0e-5c4b-44ad-c611-b37982820300/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5296296296296297\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1088\" data-height=\"576\" data-imgfileid=\"100033890\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"3\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a4e9f830-35e3-4b8f-a215-759987ab5f00/public\" _width=\"677px\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"2\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: 677px !important;\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.6em; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(143, 149, 158); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">The Information 整理的华人团队的 Agent 产品</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.6em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">「Generative AI 正在从前沿科学转向工程落地——这正是华人的优势所在，」明势创投的董事总经理杨慕融表示，该基金投资了 Lovart 以及其他华人背景开发 AI 产品的公司。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.6em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">这些公司的创始人正努力避免因各种风险问题而像 TikTok、Shein 和 Temu 一样遭遇严格审查。为了将此类风险降至最低，这些初创公司正在新加坡等地区设立总部。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.6em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">例如，Manus 的总部已于五月迁至新加坡。此外，Manus 还在加州和东京开设了办公室。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.6em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">Lovart 是一家总部位于旧金山的公司。根据其网站和社交媒体资料，Flowith 和 Fellou 也表示他们是位于加州的初创公司。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.6em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">据一名员工透露，Genspark 总部设在新加坡和加州的 Palo Alto，公司目前有 24 名员工。</span></span></p>\n  <div class=\"weui-msg\">\n  </div>\n \n",
